'''天主教显圣容堂'''（{{lang|en|Church of the Transfiguration}}）是[[纽约市|纽约市]]的一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]本堂区圣堂，位于[[曼哈顿华埠|曼哈顿华埠]]的[[勿街|勿街]]（Mott Street）25号<ref>''[http://books.google.com/books?id=qO0bAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA390&lpg=PA390&dq=San+Salvatore%2BChurch%2BManhattan&source=bl&ots=L-2tZgKYis&sig=UHM-sdTdh5FUzN-dD-XXRhY_iQE&hl=en&ei=IcvaTZi7BuTo0QH80sj8Aw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CE0Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=San%20Salvatore%2BChurch%2BManhattan&f=false The World Almanac 1892 and Book of Facts] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=qO0bAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA390&lpg=PA390&dq=San+Salvatore%2BChurch%2BManhattan&source=bl&ots=L-2tZgKYis&sig=UHM-sdTdh5FUzN-dD-XXRhY_iQE&hl=en&ei=IcvaTZi7BuTo0QH80sj8Aw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CE0Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=San%20Salvatore%2BChurch%2BManhattan&f=false |date=20200611060415 }}'' (New York: Press Publishing, 1892), p.390.</ref>，属于[[天主教纽约总教区|天主教纽约总教区]]，由[[玛利诺外方传教会|玛利诺外方传教会]]管理。今天是纽约市最古老的天主教堂建筑。 

这座教堂兴建于1801年，乔治式建筑，最初属于锡安英语路德会<ref name=nycland>{{cite nycland}}, p.45</ref>，后来改宗[[美国圣公会|美国圣公会]]，名为圣公会锡安堂（''Zion Protestant Episcopal Church''）。1815年大火后重建。<ref>[http://daytoninmanhattan.blogspot.com/2011/02/1801-catholic-church-of-transfiguration.html "The 1801 Catholic Church of the Transfiguration – 25 Mott Street"] {{Wayback|url=http://daytoninmanhattan.blogspot.com/2011/02/1801-catholic-church-of-transfiguration.html |date=20201021123209 }} from ''Daytonian in Manhattan'' (February 18, 2011)</ref>

19世纪40年代，许多欧洲新移民，尤其是贫穷的爱尔兰天主教徒来到该堂区范围[[Five_Points|Five Points]]，而早期的新教居民移居到城北。1853年，圣公会将此堂出售给1827年成立的罗马天主教移民教堂<ref name=Lafort>Remigius Lafort, S.T.D., Censor, ''[http://books.google.com/books?id=KL4YAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA378 The Catholic Church in the United States of America: Undertaken to Celebrate the Golden Jubilee of His Holiness, Pope Pius X. Volume 3: The Province of Baltimore and the Province of New York, Section 1: Comprising the Archdiocese of New York and the Diocese of Brooklyn, Buffalo and Ogdensburg Together with some Supplementary Articles on Religious Communities of Women.] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=KL4YAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA378 |date=20140101051603 }}''. (New York City: The Catholic Editing Company, 1914), p.378.</ref>，服务于贫穷的爱尔兰天主教徒<ref name=fromatoz>{{cite fromatoz}}, p.275</ref>。后来服务于意大利人以及华人移民<ref>[http://www.transfigurationnyc.org/parish/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=50&Itemid=65&lang=en "Parish history"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.transfigurationnyc.org/parish/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=50&Itemid=65&lang=en |date=20160729113446 }}, Transfiguration parish website</ref>。  

该堂是[[下东城|下东城]]四座石砌教堂之一<ref name=nycland /><ref name=aia>{{cite AIA4}}, p. 82</ref>。

1996年，该堂列为纽约市地标，1980年列入[[国家史迹名录|国家史迹名录]]。

今天，该堂是一个华人天主教堂区，信徒几乎全部是华人。主日弥撒使用英语、粤语和普通话。拥有在华传教传统的[[玛利诺外方传教会|玛利诺外方传教会]]神父管理该堂。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.maryknoll.org/ |title=Maryknoll website |access-date=2021-09-02 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225173627/https://www.maryknoll.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

